      "representation": "view",
      "value": "<div class=\"contentLayout2\"><style>[data-colorid=y6n3xq0b6d]{color:#4c9aff} html[data-color-mode=dark] [data-colorid=y6n3xq0b6d]{color:#004eb3}[data-colorid=t9bc8pbsrq]{color:#4c9aff} html[data-color-mode=dark] [data-colorid=t9bc8pbsrq]{color:#004eb3}[data-colorid=i6h0wvsyzu]{color:#4c9aff} html[data-color-mode=dark] [data-colorid=i6h0wvsyzu]{color:#004eb3}</style>\n<div class=\"columnLayout two-equal\" data-layout=\"two-equal\">\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<p><strong><span data-colorid=\"i6h0wvsyzu\">Resource</span></strong>: HDRI</p><p><strong><span data-colorid=\"t9bc8pbsrq\">Captured by</span></strong>: <a class=\"external-link\" href=\"http://www.dylansisson.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Dylan Sisson</a></p><p><strong><span data-colorid=\"y6n3xq0b6d\">Use</span></strong>: Attach this map to a PxrDomeLight</p></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<a class=\"external-link\" href=\"https://assets.renderman.pixar.com/resources/annecy_hdri/2725_annecy_hdri.zip\" rel=\"nofollow\"><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-right-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-right\" alt=\"b764f225-9112-4313-ba5a-1f74750b8767.png\" width=\"200\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/608436284/b764f225-9112-4313-ba5a-1f74750b8767.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1758284865556&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=200&amp;height=47\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/608436284/b764f225-9112-4313-ba5a-1f74750b8767.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1758284865556&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"68\" data-width=\"286\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"608436306\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"b764f225-9112-4313-ba5a-1f74750b8767.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"608436284\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"3\" data-media-id=\"b4a4ea4e-8bc3-4a54-b22f-1b9cb0e4ea26\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/608436284/b764f225-9112-4313-ba5a-1f74750b8767.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1758284865556&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=286&amp;height=68 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/608436284/b764f225-9112-4313-ba5a-1f74750b8767.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1758284865556&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=200&amp;height=47 1x\" /></span></a><p /></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"columnLayout fixed-width\" data-layout=\"fixed-width\">\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<hr /><h1 id=\"Lacd'Annecy-Overview\">Overview</h1><p>Location: Annecy, France</p><p>This HDRI was captured at Le Champs de Mars in Annecy, France, on a sunny day. If you pay close attention, you can almost smell the raclette.</p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"annecy_preview.jpg\" width=\"760\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/608436284/annecy_preview.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1758284965381&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=760&amp;height=231\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/608436284/annecy_preview.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1758284965381&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"584\" data-width=\"1920\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"607912332\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"annecy_pre